---
title: Creamy Red Pepper Chicken with Rice & Roasted Zucchini
description: A great pan sauce can make a great dish into an outstanding one. You’ll swirl savory-sweet red pepper jam with tangy crème fraîche to make a sumptuous sauce that’s drizzled over tender seared pork chops. Simply sautéed zucchini rounds out the plate, and fluffy white rice soaks up all those delicious flavors.
